I may not be an intellectual. I can’t even pass for one. But I do NOT need anyone in Buhari’s government, including the man himself, to teach me the following: I can go on. I sat down and looked at all the indices and indicators since Buhari came to power. I tried and tried to be fair and give credit to where it was due. I wanted to be magnanimous and even charitable enough. But hey, I came to the unfortunate conclusion: THIS NATION HAS BEEN WORSE OFF THAN IT WAS FIVE YEARS AGO. And I implore any one to send this write up to the authorities and I will challenge any government official to a public debate. Let him or her come with his or her facts and figures and I come with mine. We will then see who will first call for break… Source: Facebook